- Sorting of files by date does not work
- Windows ME: Can not paste from Windows clipboard
- Windows ME: MC aborts sometimes when using F3
- Windows ME: Sometimes MC aborts immediatly when started from the desktop
- temp.bat for user menu is not unique
- Cannot copy subdirectories
- Windows XP: When spawing a programm from shell, Windows reports an exeption, but starts the programm correctly
- Windows XP: Mouse can not be used after using the shell
- Windows XP: Errors when editing commands in the shell that exceed one line 

